Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别不吱声 赶紧说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,至今为止谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我明明相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,仲村！仲村！
